[center][b]Daily Chores[/b]
[[Unlocks]] at Farming Lv20

[color=cadetblue]What Are Daily Chores?[/color]
You will be automatically assigned five tasks to perform each day.[s] 
Beta testers receive an [color=cadetblue]optional[/color] 6th chore.[/s]
[color=cadetblue]What do you get for completing Daily Chores?[/color]
Daily Chores will reward you with Ancient Coins for each task completed.
Completing all your chores multiple days within the calendar month will unlock larger, monthly rewards.[s] 
Day completion count [color=cadetblue]does not need to be consecutive[/color] to earn monthly rewards. 
[list][item][b]*note*[/b] the ten day reward was changed to 8 for Feb 2022 only to give Beta a chance to receive it this month.[/item]
[item]Next month's rewards will be at 7 days, 14 days and 28 days and will have better rewards on them.[/item][/list]
Monthly rewards will show at the bottom of the screen. 
[center][img]https://i.imgur.com/cKsjG6u.png[/img][/center]
The calendar will show how many days you completed for the month with a blue/green dot.  
[color=crimson]You cannot &quot;catch up&quot; on days you did not complete[/color].[center][img]https://i.imgur.com/FKFUB6f.png[/img][/center][/s]
[color=cadetblue]I love chores and I want to do more![/color]
You may purchase an additional set of daily chores for 10 gold, which will award additional ancient coins.[s]
If you reset your chores, it does not matter what you've already done that day, you will have to do it again.
Your first set of chores had you craft 250 items. You crafted 500 items. Your second set asks for 500 items, you will have to craft an additional 500 items to finish this chore.[/s]
[color=cadetblue]Types of Chores[/color]
You may assigned the same type of chore twice in one day, asking for different amounts.[s]
[list][item]Drink Lemonade[/item][item]Drink Orange Juice[/item][item]Drink Apple Cider[/item][item]Eat Apples[/item][item]Catch Fish (manual fishing)[/item][item]Cast Fishing Nets (Large Nets count as 25 nets for this)[/item][item]Sell Items[/item][item]Craft Items[/item][item]Donate to the Community Center[/item][item]Plant Seeds[/item][item]Harvest Crops[/item][item]Use Stamina[/item][item]Mail items[/item][item]Spin the [[Wheel of Borgen]][/item][item]Open [[The Vault]][/item][/list]Your list of tasks will show, with a red locked button to show it is not completed.  Completed tasks will show a green claim button.[center][img]https://i.imgur.com/Et8hsku.png[/img][/center][/s]
[center]To see your daily chores, scroll down on the home screen, in the My Skills section, below mastery. 
